      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The pledgemage teleports, along with any equipment it is wearing or carrying, to an unoccupied space it can see within 60 feet of itself. Immediately after it teleports, each creature within 20 feet of the space it left must make a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">13</span> Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 7 ([[/r 2d6]]) force damage and is moved 10 feet in a random horizontal direction. On a successful save, a creature takes half as much damage and isn't moved.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
